<concept id="concept_3413BBD173324104B42FB714974CABE7" xml:lang="en-us">
    <title>Monitoring <ph conref="../../Shared/Product_Name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"/></title>
    <conbody>
        <section>
            <p>In addition to entries in the standard application server log file, <ph
                    conref="../../Shared/Product_Name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                /> provides a log file of its own that helps you detect problems and identify, for example, illegal access to the system. </p>
            <p>The logging of <ph conref="../../Shared/Product_Name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                    /> is based on the <codeph>log4j</codeph> tool.</p>
        </section>
    </conbody>
</concept>
